DEPARTMENT OF CHILDREN'S SERVICES; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- GOVERNMENT AGENCIES; 
FOSTER CARE; CHILD CARE; CHILD ABUSE; BUREAUCRACY; MISMANAGEMENT; NEGLIGENCE 
</P>
