<SUBJECT>
<P>
COLLEGE ATHLETICS; MISSISSIPPI STATE UNIVERSITY; GAMBLING; SPORTS RULES AND 
REGULATIONS; FOOTBALL PLAYERS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060890-0080 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 230684 </DOCID>
