</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Service Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABC's David Brinkley refused comment Thursday on a report in the New York Daily 
News that he has turned down an offer from NBC News to anchor "Meet the Press" 
and intends to remain as anchor of "This Week With David Brinkley" when 
contract renewal time comes up at the end of this summer. 
</P>
