NBC News from 1946 until 1981, met with NBC News President Michael Gartner here 
on Tuesday when the latter was in town for the network affiliates meeting. 
</P>
<P>
"David's not going anywhere," an ABC News source said Thursday. "Part of it is, 
(General Electric Chairman) Jack Welch is a real admirer of David and would 
love to have him back at NBC". 
